<node TEXT="Visualization Toolkit (VTK)" ID="ID_171102789" CREATED="1352856642913" MODIFIED="1352856764229"><richcontent TYPE="NOTE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      VTK is an open-source, freely available software system for 3D computer graphics, image processing and visualization.
    </p>
    <p>
      <font face="sans-serif" size="12.499999046325684px" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.192707061767578px; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 12.499999046325684px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; display: inline !important">VTK consists of a</span></font><font face="sans-serif" size="12.499999046325684px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><a title="C++" style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; line-height: 19.192707061767578px; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 12.499999046325684px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-position: initial initial; text-decoration: initial; text-transform: none; background-repeat: repeat" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/C%2B%2B">C++</a></font><font size="12.499999046325684px" face="sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span><span style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.192707061767578px; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 12.499999046325684px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; display: inline !important">class library and several interpreted interface layers including</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span></font><font face="sans-serif" size="12.499999046325684px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><a title="Tcl/Tk" class="mw-redirect" style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; colo