<node TEXT="Unofficial OpenGL SDK" ID="ID_1619547276" CREATED="1353179501174" MODIFIED="1353179845961" LINK="http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/docs/html/index.html"><richcontent TYPE="NOTE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font face="sans-serif" size="13px" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.1875px; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; display: inline !important">A collection of several cross-platform libraries, using a common build system to simplify OpenGL development. It distributes several easy-to-use libraries for GL initialization. It also has a library for OpenGL loading, image loading, and more. - Wikipedia </span></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none">
      The library components are:
    </p>
    <ul style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none">
      <li>
        <b><font color="rgb(70, 101, 162)"><a class="el" style="color: rgb(70, 101, 162); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: initial" href="http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/docs/html/group__module__glload.html">GL Load</a></font></b>: Used to gain access to OpenGL's functions.
      </li>
      <li>
        <b><font color="rgb(70, 101, 162)"><a class="el" style="color: rgb(70, 101, 162); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: initial" href="http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/docs/html/group__module__glimg.html">GL Image</a></font></b>: Used for loading image files into OpenGL textures.
      </li>
      <li>
        <b><font color="rgb(70, 101, 162)"><a class="el" style="color: rgb(70, 101, 162); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: initial" href="http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/docs/html/group__module__glutil.html">GL Utility</a></font></b>: General-purpose utilities for OpenGL.
      </li>
      <li>
        <b><font color="rgb(70, 101, 162)"><a class="el" style="color: rgb(70, 101, 162); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: initial" href="http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/docs/html/group__module__glmesh.html">GL Mesh</a></font></b>: Used for sending vertex data to OpenGL.
      </li>
      <li>
        <b><u><font color="rgb(70, 101, 162)"><a class="el" style="color: rgb(70, 101, 162); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline" href="http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/docs/html/group__module__glm.html">OpenGL Mathematics</a></font></u></b>: Provides useful math classes and functions for OpenGL, using a GLSL-like syntax.
      </li>
      <li>
        <b><font color="rgb(70, 101, 162)"><a class="el" style="color: rgb(70, 101, 162); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: initial" href="http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/docs/html/group__module__glfw.html">GLFW</a></font></b>: A tool for creating and managing an OpenGL window. It can be used to handle input.
      </li>
      <li>
        <b><font color="rgb(70, 101, 162)"><a class="el" style="color: rgb(70, 101, 162); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: initial" href="http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/docs/html/group__module__freeglut.html">FreeGLUT</a></font></b>: A tool for creating and managing an OpenGL window. It can be used to handle input, as well as render a few basic shapes.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none">
      Supported development environments are:
    </p>
    <ul style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none">
      <li>
        Visual Studio 2008 and 2010, including express editions
      </li>
      <li>
        GNU Make, including Cygwin and MinGW
      </li>
      <li>
        Code::Blocks
      </li>
      <li>
        CodeLite
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Also, <font face="Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif" size="12px" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; display: inline !important">the build system used for the SDK is the</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span></font><font face="Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif" size="12px" color="rgb(70, 101, 162)"><a style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(70, 101, 162); line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: initial; text-transform: none" href="http://industriousone.com/premake">Premake utility</a></font><font face="Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif" size="12px" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span style="font-variant: normal; text-align: start; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: Lucida Grande, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; display: inline !important">, version 4.3 or later.</span></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
